metadata.name: Candy Vase Club
metadata.description:
Candy Vase Club Genesis is an art focused, passion project by two brothers, Nicky and Frankie, who have worked for Disney, Marvel, Sesame Street and more.

Each Candy Vase is a combination of animated and still NFTs, based on which ranking you get! The genesis collection is a collection of 200, with each NFT being done by hand, and done with a purpose, not just a randomly generated NFT. Holding a genesis will come with a lot of perks! We Welcome you to the Candy Vase Club!
